{"tid":36454,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普爸B反擊加利佬：評論不值一聽","createTime":"2016-12-12T17:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T11:49:07.000Z","uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66507e3ddaf5457c5819381031dfb190276b0d27","tid":36454,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"前曼聯球員加利尼維利近日與利物浦門將卡利奧斯近日爆發罵戰，「加利佬」表示對方非一名穩健的門將，而後者亦還擊指對方領軍能力差。最近連「紅軍」領隊高普也加入戰團，直斥對方作為領隊的表現欠佳，故其評論沒參考價值，而且喜歡針對利物浦。<br />\n<br />\n列納：迪哥收咗火冇得頂<br />\n<br />\n紅軍門將卡利奧斯早前對般尼茅夫一戰出現失誤，間接令球隊輸波，事後加利佬批評該德國門將表現，雙方隨即隔空互轟。而作為卡利奧斯的領隊，高普明顯不甘手下球員被針對，故亦開腔還擊：「首先，我的工作是要盡力保護球員，不過在場上他們只可靠自己，我總不能在比賽中陪在他身邊給予指示。他們有心理準備好面對不同的批評，這在足球界很正常，所以對這些事我一點也不驚訝。很多評論員以前也是球員，或者他們已經忘記了被批評的感覺，特別是尼維利兄弟。」<br />\n<br />\n之後高普更直接「抽擊」加利佬領軍成績欠佳一事，他道：「尼維利兄弟其中一人作為教練，他應該明白到太過火的批評其實無助球員改進，但很明顯他的意圖不是讓利物浦球員更上一層樓。作為領隊，其實他的工作就是要判斷球員的好壞，但他明顯做得不是很好，那為什麼我們還要聽他的評論？所以我唯一的做法就是無視他。很明顯尼維利兄弟都不喜歡紅軍，他們也樂於為我們製造麻煩。」"},{"pid":"9b341cbf4fa3552ed85d7059fc7e05bac6fa657a","tid":36454,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T00:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N85704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N85704.jpg&h=4e2e41dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43c28dd43e13dad6fc31ca413f0391f5fa671d70","tid":36454,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"被害妄想症"},{"pid":"697f38a9895c29b448d7b6cf2a5f466ac5ce5a2d","tid":36454,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"加利佬仲敢9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbc877cb672b134cd04415df7f4892049507950","tid":36454,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:47:47.000Z","msg":"烏龍查都有評論佢垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa31a91882eb382d9989cbd67bbe627094ef5fbb","tid":36454,"uid":14201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"講波佬而家係教練咩 洗鬼理佢感受<br />\n好就讚 廢就彈架啦"},{"pid":"718f1a20a8b4da695b97c0e94fb9755a8bb0c1a4","tid":36454,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N85704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N85704.jpg&h=4e2e41dc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係幾明佢地兩個做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd3707ab2af0934a2eddd6f8c5941c59c47564e","tid":36454,"uid":1984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加利佬仲敢9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個球評家都有做到好教練咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b36f5317fd3e70a8ce27989e9e0e45c3c4bb12","tid":36454,"uid":28378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N85704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N85704.jpg&h=4e2e41dc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係幾明佢地兩個做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e42856ad6d87f475a8e5245a05bb796cc9cfd3","tid":36454,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N85704.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N85704.jpg&h=4e2e41dc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f9303854ffb26e9c59bd7ead1fdd15e6be224d","tid":36454,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl